<br>
to set the scene to this post I planned to try kill ixiblat and ragefire a week and a half ago, he was killed (some say after i posted intent some after but thats not really important now) and was not up so we killed 3 ixiblats for myself, hevenlee and afferado who were there and ready, but rage still didnt show till 6 hours after we left so we missed him.<br>
<br>
so i set about camping his spot, i logged there last night, i was there a good few hours today alone 90% of the time, including when to my suprise he popped right infront of my eyes!<br>
<br>
GREAT! i start sending tells to friends and enlisting a force to come kill him, unfortunately a few minutes later a member of awakened souls (who had killed him the 2 previous pops i refer to) zoned in and so they start getting a force to kill him as well again.<br>
<br>
I had gotten 12 pple in the zone by the time they had 7 or 8 and politely asked the raid leader if since they killed him at least the last twice and i had been there first with a sizeable (not kill capable) force they would back down and let us prepare in peace and time not rushing and get my epic piece, to which i was told no we are going to kill him.<br>
<br>
So i keep gathering my friends to kill him, we had 20 in the zone within a few minutes and would have been capable of killing him with ease if allowed the extra few minutes to get everyone else in and buffed when they pulled him and killed him.<br>
<br>
This wasnt technically a kill steal as he hadnt been engaged, but i amongst those who had come to help me (a gathering of ple from several guilds including as ma Gore from fire and fury who offered his help very nicely thanks gore and everyone) were disgusted at this behavior.<br>
<br>
I thought this server was made of decent pple and the uber guilds which get bad names elswhere were different here (uber meaning larger and more powerful) and as members of fire and fury who turned up to help here and against ixiblat and resolution who helped with ixiblat and would have with rage if not raiding at the time show, here they are decent and courteous and helpful, except it seems awakened souls.<br>
<br>
DO i not being in a large guild and capable of going /gu rage is up come kill it and instea have to do /tell dozens of pple and organise it more , thus needing more than 5 mins not deserve a chance to kill a spawn when quite capable, even when there first just because a more powerful guild comes along ??<br>
<br>
What would this have meant to them, a 3rd (or more) clerics with epics, to my guild it would have been 1, to the open raid community (and i know i dont go on all there are several a week now, but i go on a lot) it would have been 1<br>
<br>
I go out of my way often to help people, getting tells to come help on a raid wipe, like in sebilis, tofs, lower guk... i do passing rezzes when i see dead pple in zones equipped who are online, i went to COM to rescue a poor guy who forgot he was bound there and gated ad went afk to come back to 40 bodies (thanks faira and johanna for helping my lack of epic made it slow otherwise). An epic for the open raid community would make raids so much better, but simply because it would take me 20 mins not 5 to get a force there and prepped , even when im there alone as he pops, i cant get my drop.<br>
<br>
I shortly after this incident got tells from pple as well claiming awakened souls said you all logged so they pulled him, and from others sayig awakend souls said you tried to kill steal him. Well there were a lot of us there from several guilds, i wont name any but i hope that some will post the truth.<br>
<br>
Basically im saying i put in the effort, was there first prepping but since it takes more than a few mins i am not able to get the fight simply because awakened souls pull him sooner just because they can. Did they ks? techically no. Were they discoureous to someone there first yes. Did they have use for the epic drop yes. But would it really have been a loss for them to wait on a 3rd (or more) epic cleric for a week since they can so easilly get it at will compared to 0 in my guild, 0 in open community and difficulty getting the force there in 5 mins? not at all!<br>
<br>
thankyou for reading this post feel free to post what you will, i will not be responding to any comments regardless of the flames im sure i will get , but i do know i am very far from alone with incidents such as these against awakened souls, the kind of guild that give big guilds elsewhere a bad name i thought we didnt have any of here, guess i was wrong on 1 count. Do they have good members? undoubtedly i count 2 friends i have fought alongside and will continue to do so, but as a guild, sorry but i will have nothing to do with them.<br>
<br>
